## 1. Introduction

### 1.1 Scope

Nâng cấp hệ thống Knowledge Base (MemoryEngine) từ mức đánh giá ~62% lên 100% theo tiêu chuẩn kb-standard.md. Hệ thống hiện tại là Python MemoryEngine sử dụng SQLite + FTS5 + vector + graph, cung cấp 12 MCP tools với 3,022 entries, 571 edges, 1,367 vectors, 4 tiers.

Phạm vi bao gồm nâng cấp toàn bộ 5 Pillars: 1. Findability & Searchability (75% → 100%) 2. Content Quality & Structure (65% → 100%) 3. Governance & Lifecycle (45% → 100%) 4. UX & Integration (55% → 100%) 5. AI-Ready (85% → 100%)

### 1.2 Out of Scope

* Migration sang database khác (PostgreSQL, MongoDB)
* Thay đổi MCP protocol hoặc transport layer
* Multi-tenant support
* Mobile app
* Paid/commercial features

## 2. Business Requirements

### 2.1 User Stories (16 stories across 5 sprints)

| # | Story | Priority | Ticket |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| 1 | Real Consolidation Engine (Promote/Demote/Merge) | MUST HAVE | KSA-69 |
| 2 | Staleness Detection & Auto-Archive | MUST HAVE | KSA-70 |
| 3 | Owner/Reviewer Assignment & RBAC | SHOULD HAVE | KSA-71 |
| 4 | Scheduled Review Reminders | SHOULD HAVE | KSA-72 |
| 5 | Template Enforcement Engine | MUST HAVE | KSA-73 |
| 6 | Content Quality Scoring & Validation | MUST HAVE | KSA-74 |
| 7 | Rich Media Support (Attachments) | SHOULD HAVE | KSA-75 |
| 8 | Auto-Suggestions & Related Entries | MUST HAVE | KSA-76 |
| 9 | Faceted Search with Tag Taxonomy | SHOULD HAVE | KSA-77 |
| 10 | Search Analytics & Query Optimization | SHOULD HAVE | KSA-78 |
| 11 | Citation Tracking & Source Attribution | SHOULD HAVE | KSA-79 |
| 12 | Confidence Scoring for Search Results | SHOULD HAVE | KSA-80 |
| 13 | Feedback Loop (Thumbs Up/Down) | SHOULD HAVE | KSA-81 |
| 14 | Web Viewer UI for Knowledge Base | COULD HAVE | KSA-82 |
| 15 | Slack/Teams Bot Integration | COULD HAVE | KSA-83 |
| 16 | KB Health Dashboard & Metrics | SHOULD HAVE | KSA-84 |

## 3. Dependencies

* Python MemoryEngine (stable)
* SQLite FTS5
* Vector embeddings
* Graph database (SQLite)
* kb-standard.md evaluation criteria
* Sprint dependencies: S1→S2→S3→S4→S5

## 4. Non-Functional Requirements

| Category | Requirement |
| --- | --- |
| Performance | Search < 500ms, Consolidation < 30s, Quality scoring < 100ms |
| Scalability | 10,000+ entries, 25+ MCP tools |
| Security | RBAC enforcement, Audit trail |
| Availability | 99.9% uptime |

## 5. Risks

| Risk | Impact | Mitigation |
| --- | --- | --- |
| Consolidation merge corrupts data | High | Dry-run mode, backup before merge |
| Quality scoring too strict | Medium | Start with WARN mode |
| Web UI scope creep | Medium | Read-only only in v1 |
| Breaking changes to MCP tools | High | Backward-compatible API |

